<plot>When Martha's boyfriend Alex dies after an argument, she's left grief-stricken and pondering whether if they'd started afresh, the relationship could have worked out differently. A few days later, she's woken from a deep sleep by a late-night TV documentary and gets the chance to find out the answer to that very question.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?571665</url></doc>
